      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it clearly shows its age and mileage. The exterior features several visible scratches, minor dings, and some fading paint on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and wear on the driver's seat, but all electronics and climate controls remain functional. While the engine and transmission are operational, the car would benefit from a routine service soon to address minor suspension noise. This is an honest, high-mileage vehicle perfect for someone needing reliable transportation without the price tag of a newer model.",
