    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a fantastic ride. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable daily driver that still looks great on the road. It\u2019s got a little bit of character from regular use, but it's been well-loved and is ready to go today. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out with any questions!",
