      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014runs like a dream and has been super reliable for all my trips. It\u2019s not brand new, of course, but it\u2019s been well-cared for and is totally ready to hit the road with someone new! It\u2019s a great balance of comfort and performance. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
