      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused example featuring a high-revving naturally aspirated powertrain paired with a crisp 6-speed close-ratio manual transmission. This vehicle maintains excellent mechanical integrity, with the longitudinal engine delivering linear torque across the rev range and a factory-spec limited-slip differential ensuring optimal power delivery through the rear wheels. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing double-wishbone architecture for precise turn-in and high-speed stability. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the chassis rigidity and drivetrain synchronicity are superb. Recent service includes a comprehensive fluid flush and an inspection of the valvetrain and cooling system, ensuring this machine is ready for spirited canyon carving or track-day duty.",
